Ranger Help for: quickshot
==========================

SYNTAX:      quickshot <target>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     variable
SKILL TYPE:  archery

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to snap off a rapid bow shot at a target.
Quickshot trades damage for speed, allowing faster attacks than longshot.
The SP cost varies based on the Ranger's archery level. The Ranger must
have a bow wielded and an arrow readied. Quickshot is ideal for weaker
opponents or situations where sustained damage output is more important
than single-shot power. It has a shorter cooldown than other bow skills.
